{"tid":1070914,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姜丹尼爾方面：「LM違反了專屬合約，所以申請臨時處理，對不起粉絲。」","createTime":"2019-03-21T04:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T10:48:29.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4d9f1cc29df1af31bb6be33ab4140fa26190a7cb","tid":1070914,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:04:46.000Z","msg":"【NEWSEN】21日，姜丹尼爾法律代理人方面表示，以LM為對象，向首爾中央地方法院提出了「停止專屬合約效力臨時處分申請」。負責此案的律師表示，「LM娛樂在未事先徵得姜丹尼爾同意的情況下，就擅自簽訂了將姜丹尼爾的專屬合約上的各種權利有償轉讓給第三方的共同事業合約，正面違反了專屬合約，因此申請臨時處理。」<br />\n<br />\n他解釋說：「通常臨時處理會在1～2個月左右迅速做出決定，如果做出引用決定，姜丹尼爾可以進行單獨的演藝活動。姜丹尼爾對事態發展到法律爭論階段感到非常遺憾，也對愛護自己的粉絲們表示非常抱歉，同時表達了希望此次事件能夠早日圓滿結束的意願」。<br />\n<br />\n原來係比人賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前班FANS重話係SNS問題 唔關解約事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1044976/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1044976/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n所以話唔好好似班JYP員工咁扮知晒D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a914217850a6b967d2592e086060b31bf6e744aa","tid":1070914,"uid":198607,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:15:37.000Z","msg":"叫咗somi唔好去參加101架啦 佢又去 利申JYP員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bff03f0d39ac3b4e38119a217885eed800ff417","tid":1070914,"uid":223790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:15:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c34ba79179f2a0c21fe289cc93c7ead4ca006b08","tid":1070914,"uid":223790,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy"